{"tid":375584,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[師奶圍爐] 簡易煲埋一煲就食得 惹味豬手","createTime":"2017-08-26T15:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T11:50:22.000Z","uid":116785,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80a257da2fbe2113a535d6fe4c95d4417b154ab6","tid":375584,"uid":116785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"之前超市減價一隻聲稱800g嘅急凍豬手都唔使40蚊，非常抵屌，所以今日決定鋤一鋤佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料有豬手，bayleaves，蘋果一個，洋蔥，燒酒，老抽，八角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2zugt8rs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2zugt8rs&h=0f070767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大隻手出水就梗架啦所以唔講咁多了，出完水換個煲隊哂啲料落去開半個鐘大火20分鐘細火就有得食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n切得都幾核突，但味道都唔錯，一餐清哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b7y6q3og\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb7y6q3og&h=1cb11a80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8523f107228a83b78a3877fc4469f84583f0c60e","tid":375584,"uid":81322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"睇唔到成品係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dacd984c20cb6a54bc730d69aad31d7288607c","tid":375584,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:35:10.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下咩味......<br />\n又燒酒又八角又蘋果又bay leaves <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf3c2cf4695f1d43b5e1a7ea5d106b3c780204e","tid":375584,"uid":140736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196538ed3c1f53d3d8bc7f193689689bb22e53ff","tid":375584,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c